txt.en: The dire ash-claw and its rabble can be found in the Mokál Rukh.\n\nYou should defeat the dire ash-claw and any other plagued ash-claws you encounter.

A bounty notice is pinned to the board, stamped with the royal seal of Gondor:

'Wanted: The Dire Ash-claw
Deep in the Mokál Rukh dwells the dire ash-claw and its rabble. The Conquest of Mordor requests an adventurer remove them.'
Deep in the Mokál Rukh lurks particularly dangerous cave-claws. The Conquest of Mordor requests an adventurer to go and defeat them.
